m/scholarly/tei-Cyc02Cycl-t1-body1-d3-d2-d3.html |encyclopedia=[[The Cyclopedia of New Zealand]]|volume=2: Auckland Provincial District |title=Howick |publisher=The Cyclopedia Company, Limited |location=Christchurch |pages=656\u2013657}} \u2013 history of the town to 1900 and biographies of some local notable people during the latter half of the 19th century.\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.fencible.org.nz/ Howick Historical Village]\n* [http://www.howickvillage.co.nz/ Howick Village]\n* [http://www.eastfm.nz East FM]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060509055247/http://www.welcome2manukau.com/tourism/Tsm_HistorickWalkHowick/ Howick Historic Walk]\n* [http://www.hlt.org.nz/ Howick Little Theatre Incorporated]\n* [https://kura.aucklandlibraries.govt.nz/digital/?p=q&collection=p20062coll1&search=howick&field=title&mode=all&conn= Photographs of Howick] held in [[Auckland Libraries|Auckland Libraries']] heritage collections.\n\n[[Category:Suburbs of Auckland]]\n", "name_user": "Agh47", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:updated photographs link", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Howick,_New_Zealand"}
